{"tid":624702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[關囝請入] 「神沙車」升呢　設QR Code為電子錢包增值","createTime":"2018-04-11T01:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T05:44:00.000Z","uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7902d7b7fc9c7454d4478a4b544b2715151ab15","tid":624702,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>「神沙車」升呢　設QR Code為電子錢包增值</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/photo/bkn-20180410125706481-0410_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180410133137\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180410125706481-0410_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180410133137&h=2c7ffce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩部收銀車增設電子錢包增值服務。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n香港金融管理局兩部「收銀車」不停輪流在全港18區，為市民提供免費收集硬幣服務。金管局今日(10日)公布，由於收銀車受大眾歡迎，加上香港使用電子錢包日漸普遍，兩部收銀車現已「升呢」，市民在兌換硬幣時<strong>可選擇用QR Code為電子錢包增值</strong>。 <br />\n<br />\n過往市民可透過該兩部收銀車，將硬幣轉換成鈔票或用作八達通卡增值。為了更加環保和電子錢包日漸普遍，現時收銀車提升了設備，用QR Code為電子錢包增值。<strong>參與的電子錢包包括支付寶香港、八達通O! ePay、拍住賞、TNG Wallet及WeChat Pay</strong>。金管局指新安排令市民有更多選擇。 <br />\n<br />\n每部收銀車會在同一地點停留一星期，服務時間由上午10時至晚上7時。局方指計劃自推出後，現時兩部收銀車已為40.6萬人次提供服務，合共收集3.4億枚、總面值4.53億港元的硬幣。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/mobile/bkn-20180410125706481-0410_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180410%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180410125706481-0410_00822_001.html&d=kecV97b1VPlVpFLaMWGaYkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ad38f8a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/mobile/bkn-20180410125706481-0410_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d37244dc7ad9c5174481b7f1aa53a2a6c39bd129","tid":624702,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"唔敢入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" clas